-- British American Tobacco Names Nicandro Durante as Chief Executive Officer
-- Colin Keatinge
-- 2010-06-24T06:04:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/british-american-tobacco-names-nicandro-durante-to-be-ceo-from-february.html

          
          
             British American Tobacco Plc said
Nicandro Durante will become chief executive officer on the
retirement of Paul Adams at the end of Feb. 2011.  
          
          


  


        